  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types to v0.4.10",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/oliviertassinari/babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types\">babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types</a> from <code>v0.4.8</code> to <code>v0.4.10</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>oliviertassinari/babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"0410\">0.4.10</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oliviertassinari/babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types/commit/3b5474380793c3d3b811fe37edd40baf12701cce\"><code>3b54743</code></a> v0.4.10</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oliviertassinari/babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types/commit/740e7ec1b3a0a6a16131f1dfc20b6dcfe5c4a254\"><code>740e7ec</code></a> [core] Upgrade the dev dependencies (#&#8203;124)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oliviertassinari/babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types/commit/15901b32e19ef500bd7e2fbbdcb0ca147ff95fbf\"><code>15901b3</code></a> Force removal should abort early;</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"049\">0.4.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oliviertassinari/babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types/commit/9c444cb50fa68c44d89071185fb98459138679ba\"><code>9c444cb</code></a> v0.4.9</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oliviertassinari/babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types/commit/c4e4dabdbb68fa3e34fb7f3f8d646928f3c2799b\"><code>c4e4dab</code></a> Upgrade to Babel 7 (#&#8203;120)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oliviertassinari/babel-plugin-transform-react-remove-prop-types/commit/179cef8b5fee0ec4dd2fa3a79f153e86b49120da\"><code>179cef8</code></a> Use babel-traverse from the Babel object (#&#8203;119)</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
